<section id="about">
    <h2>About Us & Who We Are.</h2>
    <p>Who We Are: We are a group of passionate students from APEC Schools working to spread awareness and knowledge on important issues women face today, such as gender inequality and healthcare disparities.</p>About us: Hello! Nice to meet you! We are a passionate group of students from APEC Schools dedicated to educating and empowering women. Our project began as a school assignment, but we now aim to expand it across the internet to reach and support more people, Through books, we share knowledge on how women can navigate various challenges, including gender inequality and healthcare disparities. One of our groupmates came up with an amazing product to help address these issues, and we hope you’ll support us in making a difference. Together, we can create a positive impact and inspire change!<p>
</section>

